# ── memweave (centralized stack tool — gitignored symlinks into Uncle-J-s-Refinery) ──
# Single global store at ~/.uncle-j-memory; these are machine-specific symlinks
# so the documented `mw_search.py` command resolves from this project root too.
# No trailing slash on scripts/memweave — a trailing slash won't match a symlink.
.venv-memweave
scripts/memweave
